You Decide. 成「楓」之路 Buy Tickets: http://www.hklgff.hk/film-guide/asian-focus/you-decide/ 23 / 9 / 2022 (Fri) 19:45 – Broadway Cinematheque 25 / 9 / 2022 (Sun) 15:15 – MOViE MOViE Cityplaza Director 導演：Taiki Sugioka 杉岡太樹 Japan 日本 / 2020 / 105 Mins / Documentary 跨性別紀錄片 In Japanese and English with English subtitles 日語、英語對白，英文字幕 * Winner of The Best Documentary, Los Angeles Diversity Film Festival 2020, Winner of The Best LGBT Documentary, Bangkok International Documentary Awards 2020 2020 洛杉磯多元性別影展－最佳紀錄片、 2020 曼谷國際紀錄片獎－最佳 LGBT 紀錄片 * Hong Kong Premiere 香港首映 雖然父親及學校教育從小就灌輸男生需要有男子氣概等性別定形的概念，但楓覺察自身的性別認同後，漸漸明白沒有必要為了迎合大眾期許而隱藏自我，於是決定在修讀研究生時實現自己的夢想；成為一位建築師，同時以女性的身份生活。楓更參加跨性別選美比賽，希望透過分享自身經歷，打破社會大眾對跨性別者的刻板印象。本片紀錄了楓在練習比賽過程中的蛻變及綻放美麗的時刻。 Just prior to entering her long professional career, Kaede Hatashima discards her masculine form and comes out to society as a transgender woman. In the brief respite between graduate school and her new job as an architect, she tests her wings as a woman for the first time. Through competing in a beauty contest and by giving lectures, Kaede gains attention as gifted and talented transgender woman. While in the media spotlight, she seeks an active role in expanding the prospects for other trans people. Internally, however, Kaede cannot shake the self-image of a son rejected by his father, which remains with her from childhood. An ambitious trans woman aiming for social achievement and a son secretly wishing to be loved and recognized. Grappling with these two identities, what kind of woman will Kaede design? This documentary tells an ongoing story, and captures the moment when the woman known as Kaede is born.

香港同志影展推介 踢出真我 Lotus Sports Club 柬埔寨、荷蘭 Cambodia, Netherlands / 2022 / 71 mins / 紀錄片 Documentary 高棉語對白，英文字幕 In Khmer with English subtitles 25 / 9 / 2022 (Sun) 18:20 – Broadway Cinematheque 30 / 9 / 2022 (Fri) 20:00 – PALACE ifc 導演耗時超過 5 年在柬埔寨紀錄關於 Leak – 一位愛好足球的跨性別者與蓮花足球隊的生活點滴。教練 Pa Vann 除了在 2009 年成立多元性別足球隊，讓年輕女同志及跨性別者有機會參與足球比賽；他更向 Leak 及其他無家可歸的隊員，打開自己的家門，儼如父親般與他們一同生活，傳授各種生活技能。然而，面對生活及金錢的壓力，Leak 不得不做出一個會令 Pa Vann 傷心的決定… Shot in Cambodia over 5 years, Lotus Sports Club, is an inspiring coming-of-age story that centres around Leak, a teenage trans man who plays football in the under-21s women’s team of Kampong Chhnang, and Pa Vann, the coach and father-figure to Leak and other LGBTQ+ players on the team. 61-year-old Pa Vann established the football team in 2009 to encourage solidarity among straight, lesbian and gender-diverse players. He also opened his home to the more vulnerable often homeless teenagers, including Leak, thus providing these LGBTQ+ players a safe place to be themselves. After living with Pa Vann for many years, Leak, driven by the pressure to make more money for his family and forced off the football team because of his age, takes the heart-breaking decision to move to Cambodia’s capital, Phnom Penh, leaving behind the one person he loves the most.
